beer.beer_description:
The beer that inspired our crazy journey, ours is a hop driven, full bodied and refreshing Pale Ale bursting with flavour and aroma. 

Style: Classic American Pale Ale

Malt: 
Pale Malt, Munich, Caramalt & Wheat Malt. 

Hops: 
EKG (UK) kettle bittering, Cascade (US/AUS/NZ) & one other hop variety (based on seasonal variations using the best hops available) in the whirlpool and Cascade (USA/Aus), Chinook (USA) & one other hop variety in the hopback. 

Pairing: 
The all rounder.  Pizzas, burgers, grilled meats, mussels in flavoursome broths.
